text: haey banda anak del trauv ke phdal chamnehdoeng ning mean chomnue ban niyeay tha chea karpit nasa puok anak ban rsanow tam karkamnt robsa a l laoh rhautadl thngai delke thveu aoy mnoussa lok rsa laeng vinh( now thngai barlok) . dau che neah nih chea thngai delke thveu aoy mnoussaalok rsa laengvinh bo nde puok anak minothleab ban doeng laey
